<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>&quot;Scenes from a Comprehensive Clusterfuck&quot;</strong><br />
So, what did you do at work today?</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/this-page-intentionally-left-blank">More by HarryBlank!</a></strong><br />
